ENTRY       EC 3.2.1.100                Enzyme
NAME        mannan 1,4-mannobiosidase;
            1,4-beta-D-mannan mannobiohydrolase;
            exo-beta-mannanase;
            exo-1,4-beta-mannobiohydrolase
CLASS       Hydrolases;
            Glycosylases;
            Glycosidases, i.e. enzymes that hydrolyse O- and S-glycosyl compounds
SYSNAME     4-beta-D-mannan mannobiohydrolase
REACTION    Hydrolysis of (1->4)-beta-D-mannosidic linkages in (1->4)-beta-D-mannans, to remove successive mannobiose residues from the non-reducing chain ends
